response.overview: Bettie Page grew up in a conservative religious family in Tennessee and became a photo model sensation in 1950s New York. Bettie's legendary pin-up photos made her the target of a Senate investigation into pornography, and transformed her into an erotic icon who continues to enthrall fans to this day.
response.tagline: The Pin-Up Sensation That Shocked The Nation.
response.title: The Notorious Bettie Page

titles.title: Bettie Page: la chica de las revistas
